msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc108
msgctxt "pli-tv-pvr2.2:124.1"
msgid "Paripuṇṇavīsativassaṃ kumāribhūtaṃ dve vassāni chasu dhammesu asikkhitasikkhaṃ vuṭṭhāpentī dve āpattiyo āpajjati."
